WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.668 --> 00:00:06.021
Attending the public is the main thing,
 if you don't like it, it is better 

00:00:06.021 --> 00:00:06.942
that you don't do it. 

00:00:11.806 --> 00:00:14.772
My job is serving the public.
 Selling all types of bread, 

00:00:14.772 --> 00:00:18.079
or french pastries, making them
 in the morning so you've 

00:00:18.081 --> 00:00:20.484
got to come early to get them 
ready before opening the shop. 

00:00:25.073 --> 00:00:28.200
Before, bakers had to spend 
all night making bread but now…

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:31.580
there's a big baking oven, 
this is done another way, more quickly.

00:00:33.122 --> 00:00:35.575
At least, you should do
 a short preparation course…

00:00:35.575 --> 00:00:38.880
which teaches you how to cook, 
about cooking times, 

00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:43.027
how to do it, how to decorate, 
and then the same for coffee. 

00:00:49.112 --> 00:00:51.897
And also you've always got to be
 informed about new trends…

00:00:51.897 --> 00:00:54.061
and you've got to look around, 
to get ideas.

00:01:03.581 --> 00:01:06.273
I've always worked with bread, 
but this has all changed a lot…

00:01:06.273 --> 00:01:09.125
and you have to keep up to date
 with new techniques. 

00:01:09.854 --> 00:01:11.364
New things are appearing every day.

00:01:12.744 --> 00:01:15.389
The shift, well they are long hours.

00:01:15.971 --> 00:01:18.218
But if you like it, as in my case, 
it doesn't matter.

00:01:22.588 --> 00:01:24.431
I would recommend, 
although it's not compulsory, 

00:01:24.431 --> 00:01:28.053
doing a short course about bread,
 I also think a short course about…

00:01:28.053 --> 00:01:34.439
coffee would be a good idea,
 You could even do a short course in marketing.

00:01:36.954 --> 00:01:39.806
There are regular customers, 
and as such you can get to know what… 

00:01:39.806 --> 00:01:41.287
they want and what they like every day, 

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:42.785
you don't need them to say 
anything to you, know already, 

00:01:42.785 --> 00:01:44.279
you serve them and chat.

00:01:44.923 --> 00:01:46.980
I like everything about the job. 
I wouldn't change a thing. 

